---
title: Sticky Jerk Double Beef Rissoles & Carrot Couscous with Corn Salsa & Garlic Aioli
description: We’ve got a special glaze for tonight’s rissoles - an onion chutney, dark and sweet for the Caribbean spiced beef. Pile them onto a bright carrot couscous with a charred corn salsa accompaniment.

